"bg-[#f5f7fb] rounded-lg justify-center h-64 mb-4 overflow-hidden"><img alt="Microchip with TDK logo and &quot;ICM-20948&quot; etched onto its surface" loading="lazy" width="800" height="600" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="w-full h-full onject-center object-contain " style="color:transparent" srcSet="/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fd17t6iyxenbwp1.cloudfront.net%2Fs3fs-public%2F2026-03%2Fproduct-img-icm-20948_0.png%3FVersionId%3DT7uM1MRLbWAh6T3Y_txQs_Gtz7JScfCe&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fd17t6iyxenbwp1.cloudfront.net%2Fs3fs-public%2F2026-03%2Fproduct-img-icm-20948_0.png%3FVersionId%3DT7uM1MRLbWAh6T3Y_txQs_Gtz7JScfCe&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 2x" src="/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fd17t6iyxenbwp1.cloudfront.net%2Fs3fs-public%2F2026-03%2Fproduct-img-icm-20948_0.png%3FVersionId%3DT7uM1MRLbWAh6T3Y_txQs_Gtz7JScfCe&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75"/></div><div class="flex justify-start gap-4 overflow-x-auto"></div></div><div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-8 pdp-right-section"><span class="text-sm font-medium mb-2 inline-flex items-center rounded-md  text-[#9200CB] border-2 border-[#E4BCFA] bg-[#FCF2FF] px-2 py-1 mb-4  capitalize ">EOL</span><h2 class="text-[24px] md:text-[30px] text-[#000000] font-bold mb-4 md:mb-5 leading-[32px] md:leading-[40px] font-obvia">ICM-20948</h2><div class="pdp-description text-base md:ext-2xl pb-6"><div class=""><div class="rich-text-content [&amp;_h2]:text-blue-600 [&amp;_h2]:text-2xl [&amp;_h2]:font-bold [&amp;_h2]:mt-8 [&amp;_h2]:mb-4 [&amp;_h3]:text-blue-500 [&amp;_h3]:text-xl [&amp;_h3]:mt-6 [&amp;_h3]:mb-3 [&amp;_p]:text-gray-700 [&amp;_p]:leading-relaxed [&amp;_p]:mb-4 [&amp;_a]:text-blue-600 [&amp;_a]:underline [&amp;_a]:hover:text-blue-800 [&amp;_ul]:list-disc [&amp;_ul]:ml-6 [&amp;_ul]:space-y-2 [&amp;_ol]:list-decimal [&amp;_ol]:ml-6 [&amp;_ol]:space-y-2 [&amp;_li]:text-gray-700">World&#x27;s Lowest-Power 9‑Axis MEMS MotionTracking® Device</div></div></div><div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4 md:mb-6"><a class="px-3 py-1.5 text-sm text-[#0046AD] border-2 bg-[#e6edf7] border-[#B0C6E6] rounded-md  hover:border-[#0046ad] transition-colors duration-500 ease-in-out" href="#products details">Product Details</a></div><div class="pbp-description pb-6 text-sm"><div class=""><div class="rich-text-content [&amp;_h2]:text-blue-600 [&amp;_h2]:text-2xl [&amp;_h2]:font-bold [&amp;_h2]:mt-8 [&amp;_h2]:mb-4 [&amp;_h3]:text-blue-500 [&amp;_h3]:text-xl [&amp;_h3]:mt-6 [&amp;_h3]:mb-3 [&amp;_p]:text-gray-700 [&amp;_p]:leading-relaxed [&amp;_p]:mb-4 [&amp;_a]:text-blue-600 [&amp;_a]:underline [&amp;_a]:hover:text-blue-800 [&amp;_ul]:list-disc [&amp;_ul]:ml-6 [&amp;_ul]:space-y-2 [&amp;_ol]:list-decimal [&amp;_ol]:ml-6 [&amp;_ol]:space-y-2 [&amp;_li]:text-gray-700"><p>The ICM-20948 is the world’s lowest power 9-axis MotionTracking device that is ideally suited for Smartphones, Tablets, Wearable Sensors, and IoT applications. It combines a 3‑axis gyroscope, 3‑axis accelerometer, 3‑axis compass, and a Digital Motion Processor™ (DMP™) in a 3 × 3 × 1 mm (24‑pin QFN) package, with only one third of the power that other 9‑axis devices‑need.</p></div></div></div><div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-2 mb-4 md:md-6"><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="w-full md:w-[270px] h-12 px-4 py-4 text-sm border-0 text-white font-medium bg-[#0046AD] rounded-sm flex items-center justify-center relative overflow-hidden before:absolute before:inset-0 before:w-0 before:bg-[#003a8f]  before:transition-all before:duration-300 hover:before:w-full before:z-0 z-10" href="https://dilp.netcomponents.com/tdkcorp_result.html?lang=en&amp;mode=1&amp;partnumber1=ICM-20948&amp;partnumber2=DK-20948&amp;ref=/cgi-bin/tdkcorp.asp"><span class="relative z-10">Shop Now</span></a><button class="w-full md:w-[270px] h-12 px-4 py-4 text-sm border border-[#0046AD] text-[#0046AD] font-medium bg-white rounded-sm flex items-center justify-center hover:outline-1 hover:outline-[#0046AD] transition-all duration-500 ease-in-out">Contact us</button></div><p class="text-[#000000] text-[14px] font-bold mb-2 mt-2 break-words">Product Features and Benefits</p><div class="mt-4 break-words"><div class=""><div class="rich-text-content [&amp;_h2]:text-blue-600 [&amp;_h2]:text-2xl [&amp;_h2]:font-bold [&amp;_h2]:mt-8 [&amp;_h2]:mb-4 [&amp;_h3]:text-blue-500 [&amp;_h3]:text-xl [&amp;_h3]:mt-6 [&amp;_h3]:mb-3 [&amp;_p]:text-gray-700 [&amp;_p]:leading-relaxed [&amp;_p]:mb-4 [&amp;_a]:text-blue-600 [&amp;_a]:underline [&amp;_a]:hover:text-blue-800 [&amp;_ul]:list-disc [&amp;_ul]:ml-6 [&amp;_ul]:space-y-2 [&amp;_ol]:list-decimal [&amp;_ol]:ml-6 [&amp;_ol]:space-y-2 [&amp;_li]:text-gray-700"><p>DMP based 6 &amp; 9-axis Cal/Fusion, Android M features : Pedometer, Significant Motion, Bring to See, Basic Activity Classfication, Pick Up</p></div></div></div><p class="text-[#000000] text-[14px] font-bold mb-2 mt-2">Target market &amp; applications</p><div class="mt-4"><div class=""><div class="rich-text-content [&amp;_h2]:text-blue-600 [&amp;_h2]:text-2xl [&amp;_h2]:font-bold [&amp;_h2]:mt-8 [&amp;_h2]:mb-4 [&amp;_h3]:text-blue-500 [&amp;_h3]:text-xl [&amp;_h3]:mt-6 [&amp;_h3]:mb-3 [&amp;_p]:text-gray-700 [&amp;_p]:leading-relaxed [&amp;_p]:mb-4 [&amp;_a]:text-blue-600 [&amp;_a]:underline [&amp;_a]:hover:text-blue-800 [&amp;_ul]:list-disc [&amp;_ul]:ml-6 [&amp;_ul]:space-y-2 [&amp;_ol]:list-decimal [&amp;_ol]:ml-6 [&amp;_ol]:space-y-2 [&amp;_li]:text-gray-700"><p>Drones, Wearables, IoT </p></div></div></div><p class="text-[#000000] text-[14px] font-bold mb-2 mt-2">Key attribute</p><div class="mt-4"><div class=""><div class="rich-text-content [&amp;_h2]:text-blue-600 [&amp;_h2]:text-2xl [&amp;_h2]:font-bold [&amp;_h2]:mt-8 [&amp;_h2]:mb-4 [&amp;_h3]:text-blue-500 [&amp;_h3]:text-xl [&amp;_h3]:mt-6 [&amp;_h3]:mb-3 [&amp;_p]:text-gray-700 [&amp;_p]:leading-relaxed [&amp;_p]:mb-4 [&amp;_a]:text-blue-600 [&amp;_a]:underline [&amp;_a]:hover:text-blue-800 [&amp;_ul]:list-disc [&amp;_ul]:ml-6 [&amp;_ul]:space