esponsive sensing\",\"field_key_highlight_short_desc\":\"\u003cp\u003eHigh ODR with short system latency to maximize performance\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\"}],\"field_link\":null,\"field_meta_tags\":null,\"field_product_spotlight_sub_titl\":\"Explore popular sensors for drones, UAVs, and RC\",\"field_product_spotlight_title\":\"Product Spotlight \",\"field_published_date\":null,\"field_short_description\":\"Stabilize flight while detecting obstacles, unaffected by temperature changes \",\"field_spotlight_products\":[{\"id\":\"63\",\"label\":\"ICM-40609-D\",\"slug\":\"/products/6-axis/icm-40609-d\",\"product_id\":\"63\",\"uuid\":\"b3b797cf-70f8-4185-a824-4c144b72624d\",\"langcode\":\"en\",\"type\":{\"id\":\"motion\",\"label\":\"Motion\"},\"uid\":{\"id\":\"1\",\"label\":\"admin-invensense\"},\"status\":\"1\",\"title\":\"ICM-40609-D\",\"variations\":[{\"id\":\"19\",\"label\":\"General\"}],\"default_variation\":null,\"path\":null,\"created\":\"1771476687\",\"metatag\":[null,null,null],\"field_add_other_product_specific\":[{\"id\":\"1052\",\"label\":\"ICM-40609-D \u003e Add extra product specifications\",\"uuid\":\"6a796a49-1407-4b19-9659-85de60dff568\",\"langcode\":\"en\",\"type\":{\"id\":\"other_product_specifications\",\"label\":\"Other product specifications\"},\"status\":\"1\",\"created\":\"1771476759\",\"parent_id\":\"63\",\"parent_type\":\"commerce_product\",\"parent_field_name\":\"field_add_other_product_specific\",\"content_translation_changed\":\"1771477040\",\"field_add_label\":null,\"field_add_value\":null}],\"field_applications_listing\":[],\"field_axes\":\"6\",\"field_buy_now_link\":{\"title\":\"Shop Now\",\"url\":\"https://dilp.netcomponents.com/tdkcorp_result.html?mode=1\u0026partnumber1=icm-40609-d\u0026partnumber2=dk-40609-d\u0026pq=Search\u0026ref=/cgi-bin/tdkcorp.asp\"},\"field_category\":{\"id\":\"3\",\"label\":\"6-Axis\",\"slug\":\"/6-axis\",\"tid\":\"3\",\"uuid\":\"5e6ca256-6485-460e-9b76-1d5e99e40615\",\"langcode\":\"en\",\"vid\":{\"id\":\"product_categories\",\"label\":\"Sensor Types\"},\"status\":\"0\",\"name\":\"6-Axis\",\"description\":null,\"weight\":\"5\",\"parent\":[],\"metatag\":[null,null,null],\"path\":null,\"content_translation_created\":\"1762842847\",\"field_about_us_section\":null,\"field_app_bento_section_subtitle\":null,\"field_app_bento_section_title\":null,\"field_app_key_highlight_sub_titl\":null,\"field_app_key_highlight_title\":null,\"field_application_section_title\":\"Applications in action\",\"field_app_section_paragraphs\":[],\"field_app_section_sub_title\":null,\"field_apps_related_to_category\":[{\"id\":\"18\",\"label\":\"Hearables\"},{\"id\":\"39\",\"label\":\"Wearables\"},{\"id\":\"115\",\"label\":\"Robotics \u0026 Drones \"},{\"id\":\"55\",\"label\":\"Gaming\"},{\"id\":\"89\",\"label\":\"Drones\"}],\"field_category_header_image\":null,\"field_category_image\":null,\"field_category_short_description\":null,\"field_category_thumbnail_image\":null,\"field_category_title\":\" 6-Axis MEMS Motion Sensors\",\"field_dedicated_bundled_software\":null,\"field_dedicated_softwares\":[],\"field_dedicate_software_subtitle\":null,\"field_description\":\"$23\",\"field_development_hardware_title\":null,\"field_development_products\":[],\"field_dev_hardware_subtitle\":null,\"field_explore_more_apps\":{\"title\":\"Explore more applications\",\"url\":\"\"},\"field_external_url\":null,\"field_featured_news_section\":[],\"field_featured_products\":[{\"id\":\"27\",\"label\":\"ICM-42686-P\"}],\"field_featured_section_sub_title\":null,\"field_featured_section_title\":null,\"field_featured_video_section\":null,\"field_features_and_benefits_grid\":[],\"field_features_and_benefit_subti\":null,\"field_features_and_benefit_title\":null,\"field_git_hub_resources_section\":[],\"field_github_resources_title\":null,\"field_hero_primary_button\":{\"title\":\"Contact Us\",\"url\":\"\"},\"field_hero_secondary_button\":{\"title\":\"Browse Products\",\"url\":\"\"},\"field_hero_section_sub_title\":\"6-Axis MotionTracking\",\"field_key_features_highlights\":[{\"id\":\"93\",\"label\":\"6-Axis \u003e key features highlights\"}],\"field_link\":null,\"field_meta_tags\":null,\"field_product_spotlight_sub_titl\":null,\"field_product_spotlight_title\":\"Product spotlight\",\"field_published_date\":null,\"field_short_description\":\"InvenSense’s 6-axis family of motion sensors with a 3‑axis gyroscope and a 3‑axis accelerometer on the same silicon die are the highest performance sensors in the market with the lowest noise, best temperature stability, and highest sensitivity accuracy.\",\"field_spotlight_products\":[{\"id\":\"9\",\"label\":\"EV_ICM-42686‐P\"}],\"field_sub_category_grid_section\":[],\"field_sub_category_intro_paras\":[],\"field_sub_category_intro_title\":null,\"field_sub_category_section_subti\":null,\"field_sub_category_section_title\":null,\"field_video_alignment\":null},\"field_description\":\"\u003cp\u003eThe ICM-40609-D is a 6-axis MEMS MotionTracking™ device that combines a 3-axis gyroscope and a 3-axis accelerometer designed for the drone market. The ICM-40609-D is form factor compatible with our legacy drone devices – making the transition to the latest offering incredibly simple.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe ICM-40609-D takes advantage of a state-of-the-art architecture design that enhances the IMU’s performance and accuracy over temperature, making it the ideal drone solution to control the stability of the platform during long flight times that may experience high temperature shifts.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe ICM-40609-D has a max ODR of 32 KHz, making it the best sampling rate available in a consumer device. The ability to capture data at such a high ODR allows for customers to easily find any anomalies or errors that need to be addressed during flight. The accel Full Scale Range has also been increased to 32g, allowing for substantial linear movement to be easily tracked.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"field_documentation_resource\":[{\"id\":\"8412\",\"label\":\"DS-000330 – ICM-40609-D Datasheet\",\"slug\":\"/ds-000330-icm-40609-d-datasheet\",\"nid\":\"8412\",\"uuid\":\"e54c36f4-fca3-4787-adf4-8b06623cb3ad\",\"vid\":\"9622\",\"langcode\":\"en\",\"type\":{\"id\":\"documentation_resource\",\"label\":\"Documentation \u0026 Resources\"},\"revision_timestamp\":\"1774521242\",\"revision_uid\":{\"id\":\"1\",\"label\":\"admin-invensense\"},\"revision_log\":null,\"status\":\"1\",\"uid\":{\"id\":\"1\",\"label\":\"admin-invensense\"},\"title\":\"DS-000330 – ICM-40609-D Datasheet\",\"created\":\"1774521193\",\"promote\":\"1\",\"sticky\":\"0\",\"metatag\":[null,null,null],\"path\":null,\"menu_link\":null,\"field_dp_short_description\":\"The ICM-40609-D is a 6-axis MEMS MotionTracking™ device that combines a 3-axis gyroscope and a 3-axis accelerometer designed for the drone market. The ICM-40609-D is form factor compatible with our legacy drone devices – making the transition to the latest offering incredibly simple.\",\"field_file\":{\"id\":\"1055\",\"label\":\"ds-000330-icm-40609-d-datasheet.pdf\"},\"field_learn_more\":null,\"field_type\":{\"id\":\"25\",\"label\":\"Datasheet\"},\"field_updated_date\":\"2022-06-07\",\"field_version\":\"1.2\"},{\"id\":\"2169\",\"label\":\"AN-000393 – IMU PCB Design and MEMS Assembly Guidelines\",\"slug\":\"/000393-imu-pcb-design-and-mems-assembly-guidelines\",\"nid\":\"2169\",\"uuid\":\"8c9f57db-7a66-437e-9db2-6984494fbf32\",\"vid\":\"10161\",\"langcode\":\"en\",\"type\":{\"id\":\"documentation_resource\",\"label\":\"Documentation \u0026 Resources\"},\"revision_timestamp\":\"1780333281\",\"revision_uid\":{\"id\":\"124658\",\"label\":\"jimlin\"},\"revision_log\":null,\"status\":\"1\",\"uid\":{\"id\":\"1\",\"label\":\"admin-invensense\"},\"title\":\"AN-000393 – IMU PCB Design and MEMS Assembly Guidelines\",\"created\":\"1771635625\",\"promote\":\"1\",\"sticky\":\"0\",\"metatag\":[null,null,null],\"path\":null,\"menu_link\":null,\"field_dp_short_description\":\"This document provides high-level PCB design, sensor mounting, and handling guidelines for TDK IMU Products, which incorporate a combination of gyroscopes and accelerometers. Each sensor has specific requirements to ensure the highest performance in a finished product. For a layout assessment of your design, including placement and estimated temperature disturbances, please contact TDK.\",\"field_file\":{\"id\":\"1225\",\"label\":\"AN-000393 TDK InvenSense IMU PCB Design and MEMS Assembly Guidelines v2.4.pdf\"},\"field_learn_more\":null,\"field_type\":{\"id\":\"12\",\"label\":\"App Notes \u0026 User Guides\"},\"field_updated_date\":\"2026-06-01\",\"field_version\":\"2.4\"}],\"field_embedded_processor_s\":\"\u003cp\u003eAdvanced Pedometer and Event Detection (APEX)\u003c/p\u003e\",\"field_features\":\"\u003cp\u003e32g Accel FSR and 32kHz ODR for max data collection. Best-in-class accuracy over temperature\u003c/p\u003e\",\"field_features_and_benefits\":\"$24\",\"field_features_listings\":[],\"field_key_attribute\":\"\u003cp\u003eTDK SmartMotion™ solution designed for drone market\u003c/p\u003e\",\"field_learn_more\":null,\"field_meta_tags\":null,\"field_part_number\":\"ICM-40609-D\",\"field_pins\":\"LGA 24-leads\",\"field_product_image\":[{\"url\":\"https://d17t6iyxenbwp1.cloudfront.net/s3fs-public/2026-03/product-img-icm-40609-d.png?VersionId=P6jMaZY.ztg1Hup.4jypUwc1KHVJCY_s\",\"alt\":\"Microchip with TDK logo and \\\"ICM-40609-D\\\" etched onto its surface\"}],\"field_product_key_features\":[{\"id\":\"1053\",\"label\":\"ICM-40609-D \u003e Product key features\",\"uuid\":\"badf5579-203e-4196-9949-7795159427fe\",\"langcode\":\"en\",\"type\":{\"id\":\"key_highlights_grid\",\"label\":\"Key highlights grid\"},\"status\":\"1\",\"created\":\"1771476759\",\"parent_id\":\"63\",\"parent_type\":\"commerce_product\",\"parent_field_name\":\"field_product_key_features\",\"content_translation_changed\":\"1771477040\",\"field_image_for_key_highlight\":null,\"field_key_highlight_grid_title\":null,\"field_key_highlight_short_desc\":nu