 \u003e Applications section paragraphs\"}],\"field_app_section_sub_title\":\"Ultrasonic sensing solutions from short- to long-range, enabling scalable detection and spatial awareness across systems\",\"field_apps_related_to_category\":[],\"field_category_header_image\":{\"id\":\"230\",\"label\":\"ultrasonic-tof-hero.jpg\"},\"field_category_image\":null,\"field_category_short_description\":\"\u003cp\u003eTDK’s SmartSonic family of ultrasonic Time-of-Flight sensors enables IoT devices with contextual awareness, allowing products to adapt intelligently to user presence and environmental conditions.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"field_category_thumbnail_image\":null,\"field_category_title\":\"TDK SmartSonic™ \",\"field_dedicated_bundled_software\":null,\"field_dedicated_softwares\":[],\"field_dedicate_software_subtitle\":null,\"field_description\":null,\"field_development_hardware_title\":\"Development kits\",\"field_development_products\":[{\"id\":\"13\",\"label\":\"DK-x0201\"},{\"id\":\"5\",\"label\":\"DK-CH201\"},{\"id\":\"86\",\"label\":\"DK-CH101\"}],\"field_dev_hardware_subtitle\":\"Explore our comprehensive development platforms custom developed for each sensor type.\",\"field_explore_more_apps\":null,\"field_external_url\":null,\"field_featured_news_section\":[{\"id\":\"2090\",\"label\":\"Accessibility technology with Ultrasonic ToF \"},{\"id\":\"1512\",\"label\":\" iSee smart glasses in action\"}],\"field_featured_products\":[{\"id\":\"16\",\"label\":\"CH101\"}],\"field_featured_section_sub_title\":\"Stay up to date with the latest press releases, product launches, and innovations\",\"field_featured_section_title\":\"Featured SmartSonic updates \",\"field_featured_video_section\":{\"id\":\"2095\",\"label\":\"Witness SmartSonic ultrasonic time of flight sensors in action\"},\"field_features_and_benefits_grid\":[],\"field_features_and_benefit_subti\":null,\"field_features_and_benefit_title\":null,\"field_git_hub_resources_section\":[{\"id\":\"785\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic ToF \u003e Git hub resources section\"},{\"id\":\"1049\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic ToF \u003e Git hub resources section\"}],\"field_github_resources_title\":\"Smart Sonic GitHub Resources\",\"field_hero_primary_button\":{\"title\":\"Contact Us\",\"url\":\"#contact\"},\"field_hero_secondary_button\":{\"title\":\"Browse Products\",\"url\":\"/sensors/Ultrasonictimeofflight\"},\"field_hero_section_sub_title\":\"Ultrasonic Time-of-Flight (ToF) MEMS sensors for proximity and presence detection for next-generation devices\",\"field_key_features_highlights\":[{\"id\":\"233\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic ToF \u003e key features highlights\"},{\"id\":\"201\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic ToF \u003e key features highlights\"},{\"id\":\"244\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic ToF \u003e key features highlights\"},{\"id\":\"226\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic ToF \u003e key features highlights\"}],\"field_link\":null,\"field_meta_tags\":\"{\\\"title\\\":\\\"Ultrasonic ToF | TDK Invensense\\\"}\",\"field_product_spotlight_sub_titl\":\"Explore our top ultrasonic-time-of-flight products\",\"field_product_spotlight_title\":\"Featured SmartSonic Sensors\",\"field_published_date\":null,\"field_short_description\":\"TDK’s SmartSonic™ family of ultrasonic Time-of-Flight (ToF) sensors empower IoT product development with contextual awareness, enabling the creation of products that adapt their response upon detecting the presence of the user or the characteristics of the surrounding environment.\",\"field_spotlight_products\":[{\"id\":\"14\",\"label\":\"ICU-30201\"},{\"id\":\"12\",\"label\":\"ICU-20201\"},{\"id\":\"4\",\"label\":\"ICU-10201\"},{\"id\":\"16\",\"label\":\"CH101\"},{\"id\":\"7\",\"label\":\"CH201\"}],\"field_sub_category_grid_section\":[{\"id\":\"810\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic ToF \u003e Category grids\"},{\"id\":\"778\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic ToF \u003e Category grids\"},{\"id\":\"779\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic ToF \u003e Category grids\"},{\"id\":\"780\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic ToF \u003e Category grids\"},{\"id\":\"781\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic ToF \u003e Category grids\"},{\"id\":\"782\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic ToF \u003e Category grids\"},{\"id\":\"783\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic ToF \u003e Category grids\"},{\"id\":\"784\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic ToF \u003e Category grids\"}],\"field_sub_category_intro_paras\":[],\"field_sub_category_intro_title\":null,\"field_sub_category_section_subti\":\"Enable presence detection, distance measurement, and spatial awareness across a wide range of systems \",\"field_sub_category_section_title\":\"Applications made possible with SmartSonic sensors\",\"field_video_alignment\":\"Right\"},\"field_current_consumption\":\"17.00\",\"field_description\":\"\u003cp\u003eThe ICU-10201 extends battery life via its ultra-low power consumption (17µA – 320µA depending on the number of samples per second), and is highly flexible thanks to a large amount of embedded program and data memory.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"field_documentation_resource\":[{\"id\":\"162\",\"label\":\"DS-000480 – ICU-10201 Datasheet\",\"slug\":\"/ds-000480-icu-10201-datasheet\",\"nid\":\"162\",\"uuid\":\"d9a8d384-f94e-4ffc-b2f8-a563d5426790\",\"vid\":\"9795\",\"langcode\":\"en\",\"type\":{\"id\":\"documentation_resource\",\"label\":\"Documentation \u0026 Resources\"},\"revision_timestamp\":\"1775158767\",\"revision_uid\":{\"id\":\"123783\",\"label\":\"robertvargas\"},\"revision_log\":null,\"status\":\"1\",\"uid\":{\"id\":\"1\",\"label\":\"admin-invensense\"},\"title\":\"DS-000480 – ICU-10201 Datasheet\",\"created\":\"1765970545\",\"promote\":\"1\",\"sticky\":\"0\",\"metatag\":[null,null,null],\"path\":null,\"menu_link\":null,\"field_dp_short_description\":\"ICU-10201 is a high-performance, miniature, ultra-low power, long-range ultrasonic Time-of-Flight (ToF) transceiver. Based on Chirp’s patented MEMS technology, the ICU-10201 is a system-in-package that integrates a nominally 175 kHz PMUT (Piezoelectric Micromachined Ultrasonic Transducer) together with a 2nd generation ultra-low power SoC (System on Chip) in a miniature, reflowable package.\",\"field_file\":{\"id\":\"1144\",\"label\":\"ds-000480-icu-10201-datasheet.pdf\"},\"field_learn_more\":{\"title\":\"Learn more\",\"url\":\"\"},\"field_type\":{\"id\":\"25\",\"label\":\"Datasheet\"},\"field_updated_date\":\"2024-01-09\",\"field_version\":\"1.4\"},{\"id\":\"169\",\"label\":\"ICU-x0201 EVK for DK-x0201 Board\",\"slug\":\"/icu-x0201-evk-dk-x0201-board\",\"nid\":\"169\",\"uuid\":\"7e3a77aa-0ce2-4dd4-88ac-33ca40b9d0bc\",\"vid\":\"476\",\"langcode\":\"en\",\"type\":{\"id\":\"documentation_resource\",\"label\":\"Documentation \u0026 Resources\"},\"revision_timestamp\":\"1765975762\",\"revision_uid\":{\"id\":\"1\",\"label\":\"admin-invensense\"},\"revision_log\":null,\"status\":\"1\",\"uid\":{\"id\":\"1\",\"label\":\"admin-invensense\"},\"title\":\"ICU-x0201 EVK for DK-x0201 Board\",\"created\":\"1765975762\",\"promote\":\"1\",\"sticky\":\"0\",\"metatag\":[null,null,null],\"path\":null,\"menu_link\":null,\"field_dp_short_description\":null,\"field_file\":null,\"field_learn_more\":null,\"field_type\":{\"id\":\"53\",\"label\":\"Software\"},\"field_updated_date\":null,\"field_version\":\"3.3.1\\t\"}],\"field_features\":\"$27\",\"field_features_and_benefits\":null,\"field_features_listing\":[],\"field_interface\":\"SPI 13 MHz\",\"field_key_attribute\":null,\"field_learn_more\":{\"title\":\"Learn more\",\"url\":\"/products/ICU-10201\"},\"field_meta_tags\":null,\"field_operation\":\"Pulse-Echo\",\"field_part_number\":\"ICU-10201\",\"field_product_image\":[{\"url\":\"https://d17t6iyxenbwp1.cloudfront.net/s3fs-public/2026-03/product-img-icu-10201.png?VersionId=VJ5qktlj_vdInTqOn6LHYcP35oSB8rlc\",\"alt\":\"Microchip with TDK logo and \\\"ICU-10201\\\" etched onto its surface\"}],\"field_product_key_features\":[{\"id\":\"57\",\"label\":\"ICU-10201 \u003e Product key features\",\"uuid\":\"95fa6145-5df7-4122-a32d-94949abe56a3\",\"langcode\":\"en\",\"type\":{\"id\":\"key_highlights_grid\",\"label\":\"Key highlights gr