exible integration, and proven edge intelligence \",\"field_app_key_highlight_title\":\"SmartSound features you can build on \",\"field_application_section_title\":\"Highest-performance with lowest power consumption\",\"field_app_section_paragraphs\":[{\"id\":\"4\",\"label\":\"Microphone \u003e Applications section paragraphs\"},{\"id\":\"192\",\"label\":\"Microphone \u003e Applications section paragraphs\"}],\"field_app_section_sub_title\":\"Sound smart with TDK MEMS microphones\",\"field_apps_related_to_category\":[],\"field_category_header_image\":{\"id\":\"228\",\"label\":\"mems-microphones-hero.jpg\"},\"field_category_image\":null,\"field_category_short_description\":\"\u003cp\u003eSmartSound MEMS microphones deliver high signal-to-noise ratio (SNR) and advanced features such as Acoustic Activity Detect (AAD) at ultra-low power, enabling scalable audio sensing across consumer, IoT, and edge AI applications.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eBuilt on high-performance MEMS elements and state-of-the-art, wide dynamic range CMOS technology, SmartSound digital microphones support both PDM (Pulse Density Modulation) digital outputs and fully decimated outputs, enabling flexible integration across a wide range of systems.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"field_category_thumbnail_image\":null,\"field_category_title\":\"TDK SmartSound™ \",\"field_dedicated_bundled_software\":null,\"field_dedicated_softwares\":[],\"field_dedicate_software_subtitle\":null,\"field_description\":\"\u003cp\u003eTDK’s SmartSound™ family of digital and analog MEMS Microphones deliver high signal to noise ratio (SNR) and unique features like Acoustic Activity Detect (AAD) at the lowest power in the industry, making them suitable for a wide range of consumer, IoT, and Edge AI applications.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"field_development_hardware_title\":\"Development kits \",\"field_development_products\":[{\"id\":\"29\",\"label\":\"EV_T3902‍‐FX\"},{\"id\":\"76\",\"label\":\"EV_ICS-40638-FX\"},{\"id\":\"64\",\"label\":\"SmartSoun