al-world system performance\",\"field_app_key_highlight_title\":\"SmartSonic features you can build on\",\"field_application_section_title\":\"SmartSonic sensors across every range\",\"field_app_section_paragraphs\":[{\"id\":\"215\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic ToF \u003e Applications section paragraphs\"},{\"id\":\"199\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic ToF \u003e Applications section paragraphs\"},{\"id\":\"204\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic ToF \u003e Applications section paragraphs\"}],\"field_app_section_sub_title\":\"Ultrasonic sensing solutions from short- to long-range, enabling scalable detection and spatial awareness across systems\",\"field_apps_related_to_category\":[],\"field_category_header_image\":{\"id\":\"230\",\"label\":\"ultrasonic-tof-hero.jpg\"},\"field_category_image\":null,\"field_category_short_description\":\"\u003cp\u003eTDK’s SmartSonic family of ultrasonic Time-of-Flight sensors enables IoT devices with contextual awareness, allowing products to adapt intelligently to user presence and environmental conditions.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"field_category_thumbnail_image\":null,\"field_category_title\":\"TDK SmartSonic™ \",\"field_dedicated_bundled_software\":null,\"field_dedicated_softwares\":[],\"field_dedicate_software_subtitle\":null,\"field_description\":null,\"field_development_hardware_title\":\"Development kits\",\"field_development_products\":[{\"id\":\"13\",\"label\":\"DK-x0201\"},{\"id\":\"5\",\"label\":\"DK-CH201\"},{\"id\":\"86\",\"label\":\"DK-CH101\"}],\"field_dev_hardware_subtitle\":\"Explore our comprehensive development platforms custom developed for each sensor type.\",\"field_explore_more_apps\":null,\"field_external_url\":null,\"field_featured_news_section\":[{\"id\":\"2090\",\"label\":\"Accessibility technology with Ultrasonic ToF \"},{\"id\":\"1512\",\"label\":\" iSee smart glasses in action\"}],\"field_featured_products\":[{\"id\":\"16\",\"label\":\"CH101\"}],\"field_featured_section_sub_title\":\"Stay up to date with the latest press releases, product launches, and innovations\",\"field_featured_section_title\":\"Featured SmartSonic updates \",\"field_featured_video_section\":{\"id\":\"2095\",\"label\":\"Witness SmartSonic ultrasonic time of flight sensors in action\"},\"field_features_and_benefits_grid\":[],\"field_features_and_benefit_subti\":null,\"field_features_and_benefit_title\":null,\"field_git_hub_resources_section\":[{\"id\":\"785\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic ToF \u003e Git hub resources section\"},{\"id\":\"1049\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic ToF \u003e Git hub resources section\"}],\"field_github_resources_title\":\"Smart Sonic GitHub Resources\",\"field_hero_primary_button\":{\"title\":\"Contact Us\",\"url\":\"#contact\"},\"field_hero_secondary_button\":{\"title\":\"Browse Products\",\"url\":\"/sensors/Ultrasonictimeofflight\"},\"field_hero_section_sub_title\":\"Ultrasonic Time-of-Flight (ToF) MEMS sensors for proximity and presence detection for next-generation devices\",\"field_key_features_highlights\":[{\"id\":\"233\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic ToF \u003e key features highlights\"},{\"id\":\"201\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic ToF \u003e key features highlights\"},{\"id\":\"244\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic ToF \u003e key features highlights\"},{\"id\":\"226\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic ToF \u003e key features highlights\"}],\"field_link\":null,\"field_meta_tags\":\"{\\\"title\\\":\\\"Ultrasonic ToF | TDK Invensense\\\"}\",\"field_product_spotlight_sub_titl\":\"Explore our top ultrasonic-time-of-flight products\",\"field_product_spotlight_title\":\"Featured SmartSonic Sensors\",\"field_published_date\":null,\"field_short_description\":\"TDK’s SmartSonic™ family of ultrasonic Time-of-Flight (ToF) sensors empower IoT product development with contextual awareness, enabling the creation of products that adapt their response upon detecting the presence of the user or the characteristics of the surrounding environment.\",\"field_spotlight_products\":[{\"id\":\"14\",\"label\":\"ICU-30201\"},{\"id\":\"12\",\"label\":\"ICU-20201\"},{\"id\":\"4\",\"label\":\"ICU-10201\"},{\"id\":\"16\",\"label\":\"CH101\"},{\"id\":\"7\",\"label\":\"CH201\"}],\"field_sub_category_grid_section\":[{\"id\":\"810\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic ToF \u003e Category grids\"},{\"id\":\"778\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic ToF \u003e Category grids\"},{\"id\":\"779\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic ToF \u003e Category grids\"},{\"id\":\"780\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic ToF \u003e Category grids\"},{\"id\":\"781\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic ToF \u003e Category grids\"},{\"id\":\"782\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic ToF \u003e Category grids\"},{\"id\":\"783\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic ToF \u003e Category grids\"},{\"id\":\"784\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic ToF \u003e Category grids\"}],\"field_sub_category_intro_paras\":[],\"field_sub_category_intro_title\":null,\"field_sub_category_section_subti\":\"Enable presence detection, distance measurement, and spatial awareness across a wide range of systems \",\"field_sub_category_section_title\":\"Applications made possible with SmartSonic sensors\",\"field_video_alignment\":\"Right\"},\"field_current_consumption\":\"22.00\",\"field_description\":\"\u003cp\u003eThe ICU-30201 extends battery life via its ultra-low power consumption (22µA – 318µA depending on the number of samples per second), and is highly flexible thanks to a large amount of embedded program and data memory. It is also available in a module.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"field_documentation_resource\":[{\"id\":\"184\",\"label\":\"DS-000524 – ICU-30201 Datasheet\",\"slug\":\"/ds-000524-icu-30201-datasheet\",\"nid\":\"184\",\"uuid\":\"79bd5e70-0926-4fa2-a825-ec4e32f0d5b4\",\"vid\":\"9721\",\"langcode\":\"en\",\"type\":{\"id\":\"documentation_resource\",\"label\":\"Documentation \u0026 Resources\"},\"revision_timestamp\":\"1774903581\",\"revision_uid\":{\"id\":\"1\",\"label\":\"admin-invensense\"},\"revision_log\":null,\"status\":\"1\",\"uid\":{\"id\":\"1\",\"label\":\"admin-invensense\"},\"title\":\"DS-000524 – ICU-30201 Datasheet\",\"created\":\"1766057225\",\"promote\":\"1\",\"sticky\":\"0\",\"metatag\":[null,null,null],\"path\":null,\"menu_link\":null,\"field_dp_short_description\":\"ICU-30201 is a miniature, ultra-low power, ultra-long -range ultrasonic Time-of-Flight (ToF) transceiver. Based on TDK’s patented MEMS technology, the ICU-30201 is a system-in-package that integrates a nominally 53kHz PMUT (Piezoelectric Micromachined Ultrasonic Transducer) together with a 2nd generation ultra-low power SoC (System on Chip) in a miniature, reflowable package.\",\"field_file\":{\"id\":\"1094\",\"label\":\"ds-000524-icu-30201-datasheet.pdf\"},\"field_learn_more\":{\"title\":\"Learn more\",\"url\":\"\"},\"field_type\":{\"id\":\"25\",\"label\":\"Datasheet\"},\"field_updated_date\":\"2025-03-20\",\"field_version\":\"1.4\\t\"},{\"id\":\"240\",\"label\":\"AN-000175 – SonicLib Programmer's Guide\",\"slug\":\"/000175-soniclib-programmers-guide\",\"nid\":\"240\",\"uuid\":\"ec635a74-4c8a-4d83-bf86-58f2fc6f5b6c\",\"vid\":\"10086\",\"langcode\":\"en\",\"type\":{\"id\":\"documentation_resource\",\"label\":\"Documentation \u0026 Resources\"},\"revision_timestamp\":\"1779389089\",\"revision_uid\":{\"id\":\"123783\",\"label\":\"robertvargas\"},\"revision_log\":null,\"status\":\"1\",\"uid\":{\"id\":\"1\",\"label\":\"admin-invensense\"},\"title\":\"AN-000175 – SonicLib Programmer's Guide\",\"created\":\"1767684393\",\"promote\":\"1\",\"sticky\":\"0\",\"metatag\":[null,null,null],\"path\":null,\"menu_link\":null,\"field_dp_short_description\":\"This guide explains how to use SonicLib to create your embedded sensing application. Key API functions and sequences are highlighted, with an emphasis on typical use cases. Some options and parameters, and many additional API functions, are not discussed in detail here. For more information on other SonicLib features, refer to the included HTML documentation or the comments in the soniclib.h header file, which provides a complete description of all interfaces.\",\"field_file\":{\"id\":\"987\",\"label\":\"an-000175-chirp-microsystems-soniclib-programmers-guide.pdf\"},\"field_learn_more\":{\"title\":\"Learn more\",\"url\":\"\"},\"field_type\":{\"id\":\"132\",\"label\":\"Firmware Support\"},\"field_updated_date\":\"2024-07-15\",\"field_version\":\"3.0\"},{\"id\":\"186\",\"label\":\"AN-000329 – ICU-x0201 “Hello Chirp” Example User Guide\",\"slug\":\"/000329-icu-x0201-hello-chirp-example-user-guide-1\",\"nid\":\"186\",\"uuid\":\"a5874059-6794-4cf2-b82c-535741fbd9e0\",\"vid\":\"9488\",\"langcode\":\"en\",\"type\":{\"id\":\"documentation_resource\",\"label\":\"Documentation \u0026 Resources\"},\"revision_timestamp\":\"1774273386\",\"revision_uid\":{\"id\":\"1\",\"label\":\"admin-invensense\"},\"revision_log\":null,\"status\":\"1\",\"uid\":{\"id\":\"1\",\"label\":\"admin-invensense\"},\"title\":\"AN-000329 – ICU-x0201 “Hello Chirp” Example User Guide\",\"created\":\"1766057385\",\"promote\":\"1\",\"sticky\":\"0\",\"metatag\":[null,null,null],\"path\":null,\"menu_link\":null,\"field_dp_short_description\":\"This example program demonstrates how to build and run a simple ultrasonic sensing application using the Chirp SonicLib API and driver for ICU-x0201 sensors. The application runs on the SmartSonic2 board, and it can operate with either a single sensor or multiple sensors connected to the board, and it is recommended as the first example for developers to follow when integrating ICU-x0201 sensors in an embedded product.\",\"field_file\":{\"id\":\"981\",\"label\":\"an-000329-icu-x0201-hello-chirp-example-user-guide.pdf\"},\"field_learn_more\":{\"title\":\"Learn more\",\"url\":\"\"},\"field_type\":{\"id\":\"132\",\"label\":\"Firmware Support\"},\"field_updated_date\":\"2023-02-10\",\"field_version\":\"2.3\\t\"}],\"field_features\":\"\u003cul\u003e\u003cli data-list-item-id=\\\"e9a0ec0e94129415b3a7c42ea1e5dde9c\\\"\u003eOperating Range: 30cm to 9.5m\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-list-item-id=\\\"eaef52fa6f18e505846b32cc05e34c6ff\\\"\u003eCustomizable field of view up to 180°\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-list-item-id=\\\"e7ad5b1b3ab39a0cbaae952e392005493\\\"\u003eIdeal for ultra-long range applications\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-list-item-id=\\\"e686bd53b752cec19adfe58ba25612cbb\\\"\u003eUltra-low power consumption extends battery life\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-list-item-id=\\\"eb7482f4874da5cc79d8ab0e2a6223229\\\"\u003eIntegrated high performance DSP runs ultrasonic firmware freeing up system micro-controller resources\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-list-item-id=\\\"e3f77035ddc22f8d6171d914b2d2d1fdf\\\"\u003eHigh flexibility – large embedded program/data memory\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-list-item-id=\\\"e87e260cd2fae4966bcf48649f2001442\\\"\u003eWorks in any lighting condition and can detect transparent surfaces\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-list-item-id=\\\"eff8feb0298581ab55faca1c096580aff\\\"\u003eAvailable in modules as well\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\",\"field_features_and_benefits\":null,\"field_features_listing\":[],\"field_interface\":\"SPI 13 MHz\",\"field_key_attribute\":null,\"field_learn_more\":{\"title\":\"Learn more\",\"url\":\"\"},\"field_meta_tags\":null,\"field_operation\":\"Pulse-Echo\",\"field_part_number\":\"ICU-30201\",\"field_product_image\":[{\"url\":\"https://d17t6iyxenbwp1.cloudfront.net/s3fs-public/2026-03/product-img-icu-30201.png?VersionId=RL1D5SED.6rdXsGfzxc_S3akIq7ZxjM_\",\"alt\":\"Illustration of ICU-30201, MEMS ultrasonic time-of-flight sensor\"}],\"field_product_key_features\":[{\"id\":\"265\",\"label\":\"ICU-30201 \u003e Product key features\",\"uuid\":\"c836354b-5ee6-4349-b89a-dce3813631d5\",\"langcode\":\"en\",\"type\":{\"id\":\"key_highlights_grid\",\"label\":\"Key highlights grid\"},\"status\":\"1\",\"created\":\"1766055484\",\"parent_id\":\"14\",\"parent_type\":\"commerce_product\",\"parent_field_name\":\"field_product_key_features\",\"content_translation_changed\":null,\"field_image_for_key_highlight\":null,\"field_key_highlight_grid_title\":null,\"field_key_highlight_short_desc\":null}],\"field_product_segment\":\"Normal Product(ex: Ics)\",\"field_products_thumbnail_image\":{\"url\":\"https://d17t6iyxenbwp1.cloudfront.net/s3fs-public/2026-03/thumbnail-icu-30201.jpg?VersionId=diZxhohriXVPSP88TbJh2zOv6ymD55T2\",\"alt\":\"Illustration of ICU-30201, MEMS ultrasonic time-of-flight sensor\"},\"field_range\":\"Up to 5\",\"field_related_products\":[{\"id\":\"13\",\"label\":\"DK-x0201\",\"slug\":\"/products/ultrasonic-time-flight/dk-x0201\",\"product_id\":\"13\",\"uuid\":\"5849a410-707d-48f8-8e69-830b5e89b64b\",\"langcode\":\"en\",\"type\":{\"id\":\"ultrasonic\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic\"},\"uid\":{\"id\":\"1\",\"label\":\"admin-invensense\"},\"status\":\"1\",\"title\":\"DK-x0201\",\"variations\":[],\"default_variation\":null,\"path\":null,\"created\":\"1765967021\",\"metatag\":[null,null,null],\"field_add_other_product_specific\":[{\"id\":\"262\",\"label\":\"DK-x0201 \u003e Add extra product specifications\"}],\"field_applications\":[],\"field_buy_now_link\":{\"title\":\"Shop Now\",\"url\":\"https://dilp.netcomponents.com/tdkcorp_result.html?mode=1\u0026partnumber1=DKx0201\u0026pq=Search\u0026ref=/cgi-bin/tdkcorp.asp\"},\"field_category\":{\"id\":\"26\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic ToF\"},\"field_current_consumption\":null,\"field_description\":\"$2f\",\"field_documentation_resource\":[],\"field_features\":null,\"field_features_and_benefits\":null,\"field_features_listing\":[],\"field_interface\":null,\"field_key_attribute\":null,\"field_learn_more\":{\"title\":\"Learn more\",\"url\":\"/products/dk-x0201\"},\"field_meta_tags\":null,\"field_operation\":null,\"field_part_number\":\"DK-x0201\",\"field_product_image\":[{\"id\":\"737\",\"label\":\"product-img-dk-x0201.png\"}],\"field_product_key_features\":[{\"id\":\"263\",\"label\":\"DK-x0201 \u003e Product key features\"}],\"field_product_segment\":\"Normal Product(ex: Ics)\",\"field_products_thumbnail_image\":{\"id\":\"736\",\"label\":\"thumbnail-dk-x0201.jpg\"},\"field_range\":null,\"field_related_products\":[],\"field_short_description\":\"\u003cp\u003eThe DK-x0201 is a comprehensive development platform for ICU family of products.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"field_size_d\":null,\"field_size_l\":null,\"field_size_w\":null,\"field_software_downloads\":[{\"id\":\"8424\",\"label\":\"ICU-x0201 EVK 3.3.1 for DK-x0201 Board\"},{\"id\":\"8339\",\"label\":\"ICU-x0201 Hello Chirp Example for SmartSonic\"}],\"field_specification_short_descri\":null,\"field_status\":null,\"field_sub_title\":\"Development Kit for ICU-10201, ICU-20201, and ICU-30201 Ultrasonic ToF Sensors\",\"field_target_markets\":[],\"field_target_markets_application\":null,\"field_weight\":null}],\"field_short_description\":\"\u003cp\u003eThe ICU-30201 is a high-performance ultrasonic Time-of-Flight sensor that is ideal for measuring the range of objects between 30cm and 9.5m, and offers a customizable field-of-view of up to 180º. It has a sample rate of 75 samples per second at 2 meters, and 18 samples per second at 9 meters. It comes in a 5.17\u0026nbsp;×\u0026nbsp;2.68\u0026nbsp;×\u0026nbsp;0.9 mm LGA package, and includes an integrated DSP for signal processing.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"field_size_d\":\"0.90\",\"field_size_l\":\"5.17\",\"field_size_w\":\"2.68\",\"field_software_downloads\":[{\"id\":\"8339\",\"label\":\"ICU-x0201 Hello Chirp Example for SmartSonic\",\"slug\":\"/icu-x0201-hello-chirp-example-smartsonic\",\"nid\":\"8339\",\"uuid\":\"589c240c-a9fe-426e-a6c4-ea50e025d196\",\"vid\":\"9505\",\"langcode\":\"en\",\"type\":{\"id\":\"software_download\",\"label\":\"Software Download\"},\"revision_timestamp\":\"1774281118\",\"revision_uid\":{\"id\":\"1\",\"label\":\"admin-invensense\"},\"revision_log\":null,\"status\":\"1\",\"uid\":{\"id\":\"1\",\"label\":\"admin-invensense\"},\"title\":\"ICU-x0201 Hello Chirp Example for SmartSonic\",\"created\":\"1774280968\",\"promote\":\"1\",\"sticky\":\"0\",\"metatag\":[null,null,null],\"path\":null,\"menu_link\":null,\"field_description\":null,\"field_download_file\":null,\"field_download_size\":nul