Free-Fall Detection, Significant Motion Detection, Low-G Detection, High-G Detection\u003c/p\u003e\",\"field_features_and_benefits\":\"$31\",\"field_features_listings\":[],\"field_key_attribute\":\"\u003cp\u003eUltra high‑performance 6‑axis MEMS motion sensor family with the world’s first BalancedGyro™ technology and lowest power consumption\u003c/p\u003e\",\"field_learn_more\":{\"title\":\"learn more\",\"url\":\"/learn\"},\"field_meta_tags\":null,\"field_part_number\":\"part 1\",\"field_pins\":\"LGA 14-leads\",\"field_product_image\":[{\"url\":\"https://d17t6iyxenbwp1.cloudfront.net/s3fs-public/2026-03/product-img-icm-45605.png?VersionId=0qrrp8Zc8K_Fnau7Z7PpBzcgC1Drxbw3\",\"alt\":\"Microchip with TDK logo and \\\"ICM-45605\\\" etched onto its surface\"}],\"field_product_key_features\":[],\"field_product_segment\":\"Normal Product(ex: Ics)\",\"field_products_thumbnail_image\":{\"url\":\"https://d17t6iyxenbwp1.cloudfront.net/s3fs-public/2026-03/thumbnail-icm-45605.jpg?VersionId=TaAc6wTptOxhgo48F9YyBw7ibmW6072z\",\"alt\":\"Microchip with TDK logo and \\\"ICM-45605\\\" etched onto its surface\"},\"field_related_products\":[],\"field_short_description\":\"\u003cp\u003eThe ICM-45605 is an ultra high‑performance 6‑axis MEMS motion sensor family with the world’s first BalancedGyro™ technology and lowest power consumption. The sensor combines a 3‑axis gyroscope and a 3‑axis accelerometer in a compact 2.5 × 3 × 0.81 mm\u0026nbsp;package.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"field_size_d\":\"0.81\",\"field_size_l\":\"2.50\",\"field_size_w\":\"3.00\",\"field_software_downloads\":[{\"id\":\"8626\",\"label\":\"SensorStage Software\",\"slug\":\"/sensorstage-software\",\"nid\":\"8626\",\"uuid\":\"586660d9-98b7-4782-ba80-6d22786e2f90\",\"vid\":\"10041\",\"langcode\":\"en\",\"type\":{\"id\":\"software_download\",\"label\":\"Software Download\"},\"revision_timestamp\":\"1778791673\",\"revision_uid\":{\"id\":\"124658\",\"label\":\"jimlin\"},\"revision_log\":null,\"status\":\"1\",\"uid\":{\"id\":\"124658