"195\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic ToF \u003e About us section\"},\"field_app_bento_section_subtitle\":null,\"field_app_bento_section_title\":null,\"field_app_key_highlight_sub_titl\":\"Power-efficient, accurate, and reliable ultrasonic sensing for adaptive, real-world system performance\",\"field_app_key_highlight_title\":\"SmartSonic features you can build on\",\"field_application_section_title\":\"SmartSonic sensors across every range\",\"field_app_section_paragraphs\":[{\"id\":\"215\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic ToF \u003e Applications section paragraphs\"},{\"id\":\"199\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic ToF \u003e Applications section paragraphs\"},{\"id\":\"204\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic ToF \u003e Applications section paragraphs\"}],\"field_app_section_sub_title\":\"Ultrasonic sensing solutions from short- to long-range, enabling scalable detection and spatial awareness across systems\",\"field_apps_related_to_category\":[],\"field_category_header_image\":{\"id\":\"230\",\"label\":\"ultrasonic-tof-hero.jpg\"},\"field_category_image\":null,\"field_category_short_description\":\"\u003cp\u003eTDK’s SmartSonic family of ultrasonic Time-of-Flight sensors enables IoT devices with contextual awareness, allowing products to adapt intelligently to user presence and environmental conditions.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"field_category_thumbnail_image\":null,\"field_category_title\":\"TDK SmartSonic™ \",\"field_dedicated_bundled_software\":null,\"field_dedicated_softwares\":[],\"field_dedicate_software_subtitle\":null,\"field_description\":null,\"field_development_hardware_title\":\"Development kits\",\"field_development_products\":[{\"id\":\"13\",\"label\":\"DK-x0201\"},{\"id\":\"5\",\"label\":\"DK-CH201\"},{\"id\":\"86\",\"label\":\"DK-CH101\"}],\"field_dev_hardware_subtitle\":\"Explore our comprehensive development platforms custom developed for each sensor type.\",\"field_explore_more_apps\":null,\"field_external_url\":null,\"field_featured_news_section\":[{\"id\":\"2090\",\"label\":\"Accessibility technology with Ultrasonic ToF \"},{\"id\":\"1512\",\"label\":\" iSee smart glasses in action\"}],\"field_featured_products\":[{\"id\":\"16\",\"label\":\"CH101\"}],\"field_featured_section_sub_title\":\"Stay up to date with the latest press releases, product launches, and innovations\",\"field_featured_section_title\":\"Featured SmartSonic updates \",\"field_featured_video_section\":{\"id\":\"2095\",\"label\":\"Witness SmartSonic ultrasonic time of flight sensors in action\"},\"field_features_and_benefits_grid\":[],\"field_features_and_benefit_subti\":null,\"field_features_and_benefit_title\":null,\"field_git_hub_resources_section\":[{\"id\":\"785\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic ToF \u003e Git hub resources section\"},{\"id\":\"1049\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic ToF \u003e Git hub resources section\"}],\"field_github_resources_title\":\"Smart Sonic GitHub Resources\",\"field_hero_primary_button\":{\"title\":\"Contact Us\",\"url\":\"#contact\"},\"field_hero_secondary_button\":{\"title\":\"Browse Products\",\"url\":\"/sensors/Ultrasonictimeofflight\"},\"field_hero_section_sub_title\":\"Ultrasonic Time-of-Flight (ToF) MEMS sensors for proximity and presence detection for next-generation devices\",\"field_key_features_highlights\":[{\"id\":\"233\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic ToF \u003e key features highlights\"},{\"id\":\"201\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic ToF \u003e key features highlights\"},{\"id\":\"244\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic ToF \u003e key features highlights\"},{\"id\":\"226\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic ToF \u003e key features highlights\"}],\"field_link\":null,\"field_meta_tags\":\"{\\\"title\\\":\\\"Ultrasonic ToF | TDK Invensense\\\"}\",\"field_product_spotlight_sub_titl\":\"Explore our top ultrasonic-time-of-flight products\",\"field_product_spotlight_title\":\"Featured SmartSonic Sensors\",\"field_published_date\":null,\"field_short_description\":\"TDK’s SmartSonic™ family of ultrasonic Time-of-Flight (ToF) sensors empower IoT product development with contextual awareness, enabling the creation of products that adapt their response upon detecting the presence of the user or the characteristics of the surrounding environment.\",\"field_spotlight_products\":[{\"id\":\"14\",\"label\":\"ICU-30201\"},{\"id\":\"12\",\"label\":\"ICU-20201\"},{\"id\":\"4\",\"label\":\"ICU-10201\"},{\"id\":\"16\",\"label\":\"CH101\"},{\"id\":\"7\",\"label\":\"CH201\"}],\"field_sub_category_grid_section\":[{\"id\":\"810\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic ToF \u003e Category grids\"},{\"id\":\"778\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic ToF \u003e Category grids\"},{\"id\":\"779\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic ToF \u003e Category grids\"},{\"id\":\"780\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic ToF \u003e Category grids\"},{\"id\":\"781\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic ToF \u003e Category grids\"},{\"id\":\"782\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic ToF \u003e Category grids\"},{\"id\":\"783\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic ToF \u003e Category grids\"},{\"id\":\"784\",\"label\":\"Ultrasonic ToF \u003e Category grids\"}],\"field_sub_category_intro_paras\":[],\"field_sub_category_intro_title\":null,\"field_sub_category_section_subti\":\"Enable presence detection, distance measurement, and spatial awareness across a wide range of systems \",\"field_sub_category_section_title\":\"Applications made possible with SmartSonic sensors\",\"field_video_alignment\":\"Right\"},\"field_current_consumption\":\"13.50\",\"field_description\":\"\u003cp\u003eComplementing Chirp’s miniature CH101 ultrasonic ToF sensor product, the CH201 provides accurate range measurements to targets at distances up to 5 meters. Using ultrasonic measurements, the sensor works in any lighting conditions, including full sunlight to complete darkness, and provides millimeter-accurate range measurements independent of the target’s color and optical transparency. The sensor’s wide Field‑of‑View (FoV) can be customized and enables simultaneous range measurements to multiple objects in its FoV.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"field_documentation_resource\":[{\"id\":\"8418\",\"label\":\"DS-000379 – CH201 Datasheet\",\"slug\":\"/ds-000379-ch201-datasheet\",\"nid\":\"8418\",\"uuid\":\"5e5cfd2f-d8a8-4c19-87bd-6db6856eb649\",\"vid\":\"9628\",\"langcode\":\"en\",\"type\":{\"id\":\"documentation_resource\",\"label\":\"Documentation \u0026 Resources\"},\"revision_timestamp\":\"1774523081\",\"revision_uid\":{\"id\":\"1\",\"label\":\"admin-invensense\"},\"revision_log\":null,\"status\":\"1\",\"uid\":{\"id\":\"1\",\"label\":\"admin-invensense\"},\"title\":\"DS-000379 – CH201 Datasheet\",\"created\":\"1774522958\",\"promote\":\"1\",\"sticky\":\"0\",\"metatag\":[null,null,null],\"path\":null,\"menu_link\":null,\"field_dp_short_description\":\"CH201 is a miniature, ultra-low power, long-range ultrasonic Time-of-Flight (ToF) range sensor. Based on Chirp’s patented MEMS technology, the CH201 is a system-in-package that integrates a PMUT (Piezoelectric Micromachined Ultrasonic Transducer) together with an ultra-low power SoC (System on Chip) in a miniature, reflowable package. The SoC runs Chirp’s advanced ultrasonic DSP algorithms and includes an integrated microcontroller that provides digital range readings over I²C.\",\"field_file\":{\"id\":\"1061\",\"label\":\"ds-000379-ch201-datasheet.pdf\"},\"field_learn_more\":null,\"field_type\":{\"id\":\"25\",\"label\":\"Datasheet\"},\"field_updated_date\":\"2021-01-07\",\"field_version\":\"1.2\"},{\"id\":\"179\",\"label\":\"AN-000221 – CH201 and ICU-20201 Mechanical Integration Guide\",\"slug\":\"/000221-ch201-and-icu-20201-mechanical-integration-guide\",\"nid\":\"179\",\"uuid\":\"289a2d92-2256-4ec6-b7b8-5e9827cb12be\",\"vid\":\"9499\",\"langcode\":\"en\",\"type\":{\"id\":\"documentation_resource\",\"label\":\"Documentation \u0026 Resources\"},\"revision_timestamp\":\"1774278055\",\"revision_uid\":{\"id\":\"1\",\"label\":\"admin-invensense\"},\"revision_log\":null,\"status\":\"1\",\"uid\":{\"id\":\"1\",\"label\":\"admin-invensense\"},\"title\":\"AN-000221 – CH201 and ICU-20201 Mechanical Integration Guide\",\"created\":\"1766048934\",\"promote\":\"1\",\"sticky\":\"0\",\"metatag\":[null,null,null],\"path\":null,\"menu_link\":null,\"field_dp_short_description\":\"The purpose of this document is to provide recommendations and guidance on the mechanical integration of Chirp CH201 and ICU-20201 ultrasonic sensors in device enclosures. This document will cover the mechanical design, geometry, part and assembly tolerances, material considerations, testing and best practices for mechanical integration. All dimensions mentioned in this document are in mm, unless otherwise specified.\",\"field_file\":{\"id\":\"992\",\"label\":\"an-000221-ch201-and-icu-20201-mechanical-integration-guide.pdf\"},\"field_learn_more\":{\"title\":\"Learn more\",\"url\":\"\"},\"field_type\":{\"id\":\"12\",\"label\":\"App Notes \u0026 User Guides\"},\"field_updated_date\":\"2021-10-06\",\"field_version\":\"1.2\"},{\"id\":\"182\",\"label\":\"“Hello Chirp” Example for SmartSonic\",\"slug\":\"/hello-chirp-example-smartsonic\",\"nid\":\"182\",\"uuid\":\"ce9d3a41-9653-4173-9b3f-abef606e2748\",\"vid\":\"489\",\"langcode\":\"en\",\"type\":{\"id\":\"documentation_resource\",\"label\":\"Documentation \u0026 Resources\"},\"revision_timestamp\":\"1766054662\",\"revision_uid\":{\"id\":\"1\",\"label\":\"admin-invensense\"},\"revision_log\":null,\"status\":\"1\",\"uid\":{\"id\":\"1\",\"label\":\"admin-invensense\"},\"title\":\"“Hello Chirp” Example for SmartSonic\",\"created\":\"1766054662\",\"promote\":\"1\",\"sticky\":\"0\",\"metatag\":[null,null,null],\"path\":null,\"menu_link\":null,\"field_dp_short_description\":null,\"field_file\":null,\"field_learn_more\":{\"title\":\"Learn more\",\"url\":\"\"},\"field_type\":{\"id\":\"132\",\"label\":\"Firmware Support\"},\"field_updated_date\":null,\"field_version\":\"2.31.0\\t\"},{\"id\":\"183\",\"label\":\"SmartSonic CH201 Static Target Rejection Example\",\"slug\":\"/smartsonic-ch201-static-target-rejection-example\",\"nid\":\"183\",\"uuid\":\"f8b0d267-3c8a-43fe-88e9-ff51fc157e22\",\"vid\":\"490\",\"la