ption\":\"\u003cp\u003eThe T5838\u0026nbsp;is a low noise, high AOP digital Pulse\u0026nbsp;Density\u0026nbsp;Modulation (PDM) microphone using a fifth-order Σ‑Δ modulator. It also features Acoustic\u0026nbsp;Activity\u0026nbsp;Detect (AAD), a new ultra-low power edge processing feature consuming as low as 20\u0026nbsp;µA.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"field_size_d\":\"0.98\",\"field_size_l\":\"3.50\",\"field_size_w\":\"2.65\",\"field_snr\":\"68.00\",\"field_software_downloads\":[],\"field_specification_short_descri\":null,\"field_status\":\"Production\",\"field_sub_title\":\"Bottom Port PDM Digital Output Multi‑Mode Microphone\",\"field_supply_voltage_vdd\":\"1.8\",\"field_support_and_resources\":[],\"field_target_markets\":[],\"field_target_markets_application\":\"\u003cp\u003eSmartphones, Smart Speakers, Headsets, TV Remotes, Smart TV, Set-top Box, Wearables\u003c/p\u003e\",\"field_temperature\":null,\"field_weight\":null}],\"field_featured_section_sub_title\":null,\"field_featured_section_title\":null,\"field_featured_video_section\":null,\"field_features_and_benefits_grid\":[{\"id\":\"174\",\"label\":\"9-axis \u003e Features and benefits grid section\",\"uuid\":\"c745905f-5b3c-4546-b5f5-5ab0d6113429\",\"langcode\":\"en\",\"type\":{\"id\":\"key_highlights_grid\",\"label\":\"Key highlights grid\"},\"status\":\"1\",\"created\":\"1764492982\",\"parent_id\":\"32\",\"parent_type\":\"taxonomy_term\",\"parent_field_name\":\"field_features_and_benefits_grid\",\"content_translation_changed\":null,\"field_image_for_key_highlight\":null,\"field_key_highlight_grid_title\":\"TMR features\",\"field_key_highlight_short_desc\":\"\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003eHigh sensitivity\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eHigh accuracy\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eLowest-power magnetometer\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eMagnetic field shock-resistance\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eLow noise\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eWide range\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\"},{\"id\":\"155\",\"label\":\"9-axis \u003e Features and benefits grid section\",\"uuid\":\"c7b47a9f-d258-4d4e-87cf-12544b1c28c0\",\"langcode\":\"en\",\"type\":{\"id\":\"key_highlights_grid\",\"label\":\"Key highlights grid\"},\"status\":\"1\",\"created\":\"1764493046\",\"parent_id\":\"32\",\"parent_type\":\"taxonomy_term\",\"parent_field_name\":\"field_features_and_benefits_grid\",\"content_translation_changed\":null,\"field_image_for_key_highlight\":null,\"field_key_highlight_grid_title\":\"IMU features\",\"field_key_highlight_short_desc\":\"\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003eLowest power IMU technology\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eHigh-performance MEMS technology\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eIndustry-first vibration-resistant gyro with Balanced Gyro technology\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eLow noise accelerometer\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\"},{\"id\":\"26\",\"label\":\"9-axis \u003e Features and benefits grid section\",\"uuid\":\"b50cd996-c85f-458f-a5a3-8f3ecf32e221\",\"langcode\":\"en\",\"type\":{\"id\":\"key_highlights_grid\",\"label\":\"Key highlights grid\"},\"status\":\"1\",\"created\":\"1764493088\",\"parent_id\":\"32\",\"parent_type\":\"taxonomy_term\",\"parent_field_name\":\"field_features_and_benefits_grid\",\"content_translation_changed\":null,\"field_image_for_key_highlight\":null,\"field_key_highlight_grid_title\":\"Software features\",\"field_key_highlight_short_desc\":\"\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003eOn-chip sensor fusion and precise time synchronization, for immediate processing of sensor data at exact moment of motion\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eFast and accurate gyro and mag cross-calibration\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eAutomatic magnetic shock recovery\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003ePDR application-level software for a variety of operating systems and platforms\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\"}],\"field_features_and_benefit_subti\":\"Line of copy detailing value props. This is an example of an entire paragraph  in this area to show that it doesn’t need to span the entire width to maintain readability.\",\"field_featu